{The bidding has been as shown.   

With 13 points and 4 of the "other" Major you make a Negative Double. Partner's rebid is 2\H. What is your next bid? 

Partner has 4 \Hs and an opening hand. You have 4 \Hs and an opening hand. That adds up to a game bid and an 8-card \H fit. You bid 4\H.}

